Class WebCmsAssetUrlConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.webcms.domain.url.config.WebCmsAssetUrlConfiguration

  • @Exposed
 @Configuration
public class WebCmsAssetUrlConfiguration
extends Object
    Allows configuration of a single WebCmsAssetEndpoint for WebCmsAsset implementations. A single endpoint will behave as the single collection of URLs pointing to this asset.

    0.0.1
